{"tid":1869293,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又有食人血饅頭嘅 IG SHOP，各位小心","createTime":"2020-02-08T06:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T11:36:48.000Z","uid":248656,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ce3ff6b22ecbe285c7ac3ff7b726c7675c55d99b","tid":1869293,"uid":248656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZDSQN9A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZDSQN9A.jpg&h=c8b55712&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢間IG Shop 一開始就叫人Follow佢，話followers先可以買佢地店嘅口罩。不過一直遲遲唔報價，話1/2會開賣，點知開賣嘅口罩都成二百幾元。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kj1FqUk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKj1FqUk.jpg&h=722d3b09&s={SIZE}\" /> 但都係有好多人留言同佢買（有幾百人） 到左後期，佢就將口罩愈賣愈貴，30個$375<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rsm6muh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRsm6muh.jpg&h=7fe4f54f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而一個口罩盒都成$140，都係有唔少人唔佢留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後開始有人屌佢話佢賣得貴，佢竟然仲可以理直氣壯罵翻人，仲要有人撐佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ABCmao7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FABCmao7.jpg&h=ba9343df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然買賣呢樣嘢係你情我願，但咁樣態度嘅店主仲要去幫襯？真係不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日仲要出客人同佢嘅對話圖公審個客<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1rMBJM8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1rMBJM8.jpg&h=694af514&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y6A650t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY6A650t.jpg&h=9897def3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZzDc1yP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZzDc1yP.jpg&h=546dac84&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明明個店主有問題，仲可以咁做，好彩今次有明眼人出聲話店主，不過店主又小氣del人留言，依家仲del左唔少post，好彩我有back up到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家買口罩之前諗清楚，佢個價同部分藥房無分別，唔好見到口罩就2盒thanks!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n店主電話 54836630<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rcHtzU6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrcHtzU6.jpg&h=0f1ede4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIG shop 改名record<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvcM514.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvcM514.jpg&h=51c78ebe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cae3e11451ce78f336026915be1b2a39020f2853","tid":1869293,"uid":219249,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:27:57.000Z","msg":"正想講, 本身一開始followers 三千幾. 之後賣口罩先多. <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身都prefer依兩隻, 但價錢不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tnkfe1s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTnkfe1s.jpg&h=52f63f1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RXjWJUN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRXjWJUN.jpg&h=def850b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358e660424463359ab2c1700e211db622c6a6285","tid":1869293,"uid":74468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:34:44.000Z","msg":"一開始講到自己唔食人血饅頭<br />\n唔會賣到500蚊一盒<br />\n賣300幾當自己良心商人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459a2e644b388e1f5be2803c7b091f44c968cd53","tid":1869293,"uid":76845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T08:57:43.000Z","msg":"有良心價300幾一盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89b8140c3403fa247fa1fd248452ddd62858da9","tid":1869293,"uid":248656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:24:34.000Z","msg":"依家驚到熄曬留言，又唔留價錢，正係叫人whatsapp佢，係咪做得虧心事多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LT16opp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLT16opp.png&h=b9107171&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2513ff718a347d30300aecb6633c2a809b16a0cd","tid":1869293,"uid":125801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T17:37:42.000Z","msg":"推下先，大家唔好去依D咁嘅店鋪買啦"},{"pid":"fb8176cbc22ec428c5a9425db212563453a72fc8","tid":1869293,"uid":57826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T18:03:29.000Z","msg":"Ig咁多次更新最有用就係睇到人改名紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf8ec6ae8d3ca93fdde5850d91da5cf90fe0acd","tid":1869293,"uid":248656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:47:38.000Z","msg":"推到佢收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9819a5385e9331ffd3352d09fd7d427a03c60098","tid":1869293,"uid":219249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T06:17:48.000Z","msg":"更新: 之前又話賣淨嘅口罩畀有需要嘅人而家就畀啲客, 成日搬龍門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jhbVn1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjhbVn1f.jpg&h=eb2644c7&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DcKDkNW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDcKDkNW.jpg&h=f946defc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f3855b4640519336a9240161b794549faa63fc5","tid":1869293,"uid":184370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T06:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vBJwFTg.png\" data-thumb